    "1104207": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Albedo and hear his conclusions",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Tasty? You've got a funny look on your face, {NICKNAME}!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's... burning a bit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You drank this!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#You said you tried some already! You sure it was ready? What happened to {M#him}{F#her}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Hmm? Oh, this was the result I was expecting, and a very positive one at that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "This potion channels elemental power into the body. Under normal circumstances, a repelling reaction is to be expected."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "But if the internal elemental flow is unimpeded, you'll only experience momentary discomfort. Once the flow is complete, there won't be any other effects."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So you knew you'd be sick and still drank some?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Eh-he, it was my own concoction of course, only natural for me to be the guinea pig."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Out of... consideration for the test subject?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "But of course! You're my assistant, by all sense and reason it would be wrong of me to place that risk onto you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What about the risk to you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Perhaps it's just scholarly self-assurance, and it certainly speeds things up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "In conclusion, I'd say we have our conclusion! As far as elemental energy is concerned, you're no different from anyone else in this world, nothing peculiar."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aw, Paimon wanted something cooler to happen..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Then again, better an ordinary result than a peculiar result. Peculiar results have a tendency to be of the... undesirable variety."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I feel like you're referring to something in particular..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "The good thing about \"ordinary\" is that everything is an object of reference, and everyone understands you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "People are the same, they can understand, empathize, encourage, and support one another."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "When you're sick, a doctor can diagnose you because they are you. When something goes wrong, you can ask people who've made the same mistake for their experience, because you are them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "But a peculiar person... They don't have much recourse for the things we take for granted. The essence of their life is fundamentally different."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "For example... A human can't understand the life of a Pyro Regisvine, or an Eye of the Storm. Have I explained it clearly enough?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I think I'm getting it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Still seems... like there's another layer of meaning to your words."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "To sum up, this has been a positive outcome. Going forward, you can use your elemental power without fear."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Timaeus, the results of the new experiment are out. If you could see to collating them..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Timaeus",
                    "T": "Just a moment, Sir! I'll handle it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Timaeus",
                    "T": "You gave me a lot to consider, really stretched my limits. I'm thinking a lot clearer now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Timaeus",
                    "T": "Having you down as an animal wasn't very precise of me, but starting with the premise of an elemental life form!? Now that was—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Not bad, I think it's an interesting line of inquiry. Whatever the truth of the matter, I'd like your research at the fore as opposed to my judgment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Timaeus",
                    "T": "You can count on me, Sir! I'll extract a result satisfactory to all!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is he trying to join the Knights? He's starting to sound like a suck-up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh... What Paimon meant to say was... That's the spirit! Mr. Albedo, say something..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Hmm... Before we can proceed with our research, I need to... prepare something. Wait one moment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "If you're interested, why not have a look around? It may help to pass the time."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
