    "1104401": {
        "Desc": "Talk to the returning Albedo",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I'm back. Did you see anything interesting?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Couldn't make heads or tails of anything."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Not to worry, they're all for alchemical purposes, you'd be hard pressed to find an everyday use for them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Your things aren't very organized."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Hmm, agreed. I'd love to find a moment to put them all in order. Still, experiments come first..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Well, on with the research."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "There may be significant differences between different worlds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Take Teyvat, for example. Here, those with Visions can manipulate the elements."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "But worlds may well exist where only one person is able to do so, or even everyone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "#So, leaving elements to one side... Do you possess any... unique abilities, {NICKNAME}? Ones that don't exist in this world?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I think answering this question calls for the same methodology as last time. In other words, time for the next experiment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Am I battling slimes again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I drank my fill, thanks..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "No, no! You shan't be required to exert quite so much effort this time around."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Now, see this pillar here. Use your willpower to try and break it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sorry, I just can't do it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "That was your best effort? Hmm... Well, can't be helped, I suppose."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's with the disappointment!? Isn't that, like, impossible?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon, you give it a shot."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You think Paimon knows how to do that stuff?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "That was your best effort? Hmm... Well, can't be helped, I suppose."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Ah! Have you tried using your elemental power with food? I don't mean for cooking as such — rather, channeling your power into the ingredients themselves."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I'm curious to see how the taste and texture respond. It may even help with... proliferation..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Alchemists certainly have active imaginations."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sure you're not just peckish?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Haha, I suppose I have a curiosity for things that others find surprising."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Anyway, why don't you cook us up a Sunshine Sprat? I've just finished preparing the recipe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Cooking? Paimon was looking forward to more mad scientist stuff!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Not only is this recipe a staple for me, it's also worth experimenting with and highly nutritious!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph, Paimon bets you're just hungry!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It does sound yummy though... Okay, Paimon approves!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I know what you're getting at."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'll save you a fin or two."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Mm-hmm, good buddies are always on the same page!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I'll leave you to it, then. Looking forward to the results."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "If there's anything left over, maybe Timaeus can finish the last morsels."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uhh... Paimon doesn't think we'll have that problem."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
