    "1104415": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Mm! An average outcome experimentally, but you've really brought out the flavor. You seem well-versed in the science of gastronomy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "As far as the proliferation hypothesis is concerned, we've come up short. Seems like food presents the same headaches in your world as it does ours."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Unless... Could it be that the natural laws of this world are limiting your unique abilities?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We just didn't know how to channel elemental power into the food. It's a little more complicated than adding herbs and spices, y'know!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Not to worry, at least we put some food to good use, no need to feel disheartened."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "And here's your portion, enjoy! I can box it up if you like."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Woohoo, thanks! Glad you were paying attention."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're Paimon's new favorite."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Not often that Paimon gets this much attention."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I can tell that you're good friends. Paimon was keeping an eye on you and your safety during the whole experiment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Not that Paimon would have been able to do much if things had gone wrong, but anyway..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey! You were being nice a second ago!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But you do have tasty recipes, so Paimon forgives you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And you're right, we are good friends. You have good friends too, right? Good students?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "...Uh, yes! I'm fortunate too, I suppose. Anyway, moving on to the next experiment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "There are all manner of alchemical items here, keeping them in their proper place is a challenge at the best of times. A while ago, I had the misfortune of misplacing a batch."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I managed to retrieve the majority, but two vials have been evading me: Anemo Crystalfly elemental extract and Electro Hypostasis powder."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's barely finished eating and you want us to go gathering again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Don't worry if you can't locate them. I was planning to replace them anyway, though finding them would save me the hassle."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "If you had, say, a \"superpower,\" like night vision, or vibratory sensing, lost property would be a thing of the past."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I must have dropped them somewhere in the area where you were looking just now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So... guess we'd better take a look?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There should be some elemental traces on the lost items."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh yeah! You could use Elemental Sight!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
