    "1104403": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Albedo and hear his conclusions",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Goodness, you managed to find them? Incredible, a thousand thanks."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I'm wondering, this Elemental Sight... This is what allowed you to locate the items, and find me here in the mountains, correct?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yup! Guess it does sorta count as a superpower, huh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Unfortunately, though Elemental Sight is seldom seen, it is not unheard of in Teyvat."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Only a never-before-seen, otherworldly power would be of benefit to my research."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You mean... We failed again...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Don't be disheartened, this falls entirely within my expectations. Besides, getting these items back? I'd call this a very worthwhile experiment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I have to commend your deduction that the items would contain elemental traces."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Right then. Up until now, our research has focused on your otherworldly identity. Our research on your identity as one of us is just beginning."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "With you to the end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...How do I get off this train?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "In essence, the differences between humans are reflected in our intellectual and physical capabilities. Let's start with physical."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Looking out from where we're standing, can you see what Sucrose is doing?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Nope."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "And if you jumped from here and landed on that cliff — the one over there — could you see her then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Nope."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "So what about if you planted a single blow on the mountain face here and it burst into a million fragments? Then could you see her?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Nope."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sounds like we're still on the superpower test."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Hmm, then I shouldn't get too excited. Still, we'll gain a more thorough understanding with an experiment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I know of a location that will be perfect for a physical test. Please, follow me."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1104301": {
        "Desc": "Head to the location of the next experiment",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You... You want us to jump!? From up here!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Not necessarily — not if you know of a better method, that is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'd better have a better method."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's not very reassuring."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Whichever method you choose, the experiment will end when you reach the opposite shore of the lake."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "I will factor the time expended and your top speed into my comparative analysis."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The opposite side of the lake... So... We're gonna be swimming?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Without limitations, we complete tasks intuitively using the method that seems most rational to us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Some of us would be unable to stand the icy waters... Others might find the whole thing rather refreshing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "No matter what choice you make, it's all a part of the experiment. For me, every detail is invaluable to the research."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "My kind of experiment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This is actually less stressful than the superpower part."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Albedo",
                    "T": "Then if you would, please. I eagerly await the results."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
